Mitsubishi Bank Ltd's Hong Kongbranch is planning a 40 mln New Zealand dlr certificate ofdeposit, CD, issue, banking sources said.    The three-year CDs are denominated in 100,000 dlr units andwill carry interest at 37.5 basis points below the three-monthNew Zealand bank bill rate.    Payment date is expected to be around April 1.    ANZ Securities Asia Ltd is lead manager for the issue. REUTER&#3;